						<summary>

						<p>Slab paved in the <hi rend="italic">mukhamaṇḍapa</hi> of the Veṅkaṭēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1672, Pramōdūta, Māgha śu. 15,</hi> corresponding to 1750 A.D., February 10, Saturday.</p>						

						<p>It records the obeisance of Dattayyagāri Śēshāchalam. It also mentions a certain Aṁbavaram Rāghavaya.</p>						

